1. 分宽度及其比值：
$$
\Gamma_c \;=\; 2\,P_0^{(c)}\,\gamma_c^2,\quad
\frac{\Gamma_p}{\Gamma_\alpha}
=\frac{P_0^{(p)}\,\gamma_p^2}{P_0^{(\alpha)}\,\gamma_\alpha^2}
=\frac{P_0^{(p)}}{P_0^{(\alpha)}},
$$
因为 $\gamma_p^2=\gamma_\alpha^2$。

2. 在高能极限下 $P_0\propto k=\sqrt{2\mu E}/\hbar$，所以
$$
\frac{\Gamma_p}{\Gamma_\alpha}
=\frac{k_p}{k_\alpha}
=\sqrt{\frac{\mu_p}{\mu_\alpha}}\,.
$$

3. 约化质量（其中 $m_u$ 为符号）：
$$
\mu_p
=\frac{m_p\,M_{A-1}}{m_p+M_{A-1}}
=\frac{m_u\,(A-1)m_u}{m_u+(A-1)m_u}
=\frac{A-1}{A}\,m_u,
$$
$$
\mu_\alpha
=\frac{m_\alpha\,M_{A-4}}{m_\alpha+M_{A-4}}
=\frac{4m_u\,(A-4)m_u}{4m_u+(A-4)m_u}
=\frac{4(A-4)}{A}\,m_u.
$$

4. 宽度比：
$$
\frac{\Gamma_p}{\Gamma_\alpha}
=\sqrt{\frac{\mu_p}{\mu_\alpha}}
=\sqrt{\frac{\frac{A-1}{A}m_u}{\frac{4(A-4)}{A}m_u}}
=\sqrt{\frac{A-1}{4(A-4)}}.
$$
